import React from "react"
import styled from "styled-components"
import { Container } from "./contants"
import { Title } from "./contants"
const Item = styled.div``
const Name = styled.span`
  font-weight: 600;
`
const Wrapper1 = styled.div``
const Wrapper2 = styled.div`
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  border: 1px solid #ccc;
  padding: 5px;
`
const Menu = styled.div``
const Menu2 = styled.div`
  text-align: right;
`

const Value = styled.span``
const API = [
  {
    name: "ContactID",
    value: "ABC",
  },
  {
    name: "CustomerID",
    value: 123456,
  },
  {
    name: "Agent",
    value: 26644,
  },
  {
    name: "ContactDate",
    value: "09-Mar-21 11:48:28",
  },
  {
    name: "ContactType",
    value: "Voice",
  },
  {
    name: "CallHoldDuration",
    value: "0s",
  },
  {
    name: "CallDuration",
    value: "53s",
  },
]
const ContactDetails = () => {
  return (
    <Container>
      <Title>ContactDetails</Title>
      <Wrapper1>
        <Wrapper2>
          <Menu>
            <Item>
              <Name>ContactID: </Name>
              <Value>ABC</Value>
            </Item>
            <Item>
              <Name>CustomerID: </Name>
              <Value>0123456</Value>
            </Item>
            <Item>
              <Name>Agent: </Name>
              <Value>0123456</Value>
            </Item>
            <Item>
              <Name>Contact Date: </Name>
              <Value>09-Mar-21 11:48:28</Value>
            </Item>
          </Menu>
          <Menu2>
            <Item>
              <Name>Contact Type: </Name>
              <Value>Voice</Value>
            </Item>
            <Item>
              <Name>Call Hold Duration: </Name>
              <Value>0s</Value>
            </Item>
            <Item>
              <Name>Call Duration: </Name>
              <Value>53s</Value>
            </Item>
          </Menu2>
        </Wrapper2>
      </Wrapper1>
    </Container>
  )
}

export default ContactDetails
